# C++ PRACTICALS

### Write a program to compute the sum of the first n terms of the following series:
![Capture](https://github.com/Raveena-29/Cplus-plus/assets/148243757/ae6d5855-cfc5-48c6-95ad-ba8ce7197988)

```
# include <iostream>
#include <cmath>
using namespace std;
double series(int num){
    double sum=0.0 ,ser;
    for (int i =1 ;i<=num;++i){
        ser=1/pow(i,i);
        sum+=ser;
    }
    return sum;
}
int main(){
    int num;
    cout << "Enter the number of terms:";
    cin>>num;
    double result= series(num);
    cout << result;
    return 0;
}
```
